배포 전략:       Blue-Green + Canary
모니터링:        Prometheus + Grafana + ELK
```

### 통합 점검

```
Push 감지 → Build → Test → Security → Quality Check
                      ↓
                 Success?
                 /     \
               Yes      No
               /         \
          Deploy       Notification
           /               |
    Staging → Prod    Dev Team
```

